.so fork.tmac
.SS GET_DIMENSIONS ACTION
.PP
The
.B get_dimensions
action retrieves important screen parameters including screen
dimensions and
.B pwb
output specifications.
.PP
.pt_get_dimensions
.RS
.TP
.I associative_array_name
gName of the associative array in which the dimensions will be
returned.
The array will be created if it doesn't already exist.
.RS
.PP
The index names of this associative array are:
.TS
tab(|);
lb l.
screen_lines|full count of screen lines
screen_cols|full count of screen columns
pager_lines|lines controlled by the pager
pager_cols|characters per pager-controlled line
margin_top|number of rows in head (top of screen)
margin_bottom|number of rows in foot (bottom of screen)
margin_left|empty columns left of the content
margin_right|empty columns right of the content
.TE
.RE
.RE
